title: 102001_RNAseq
characteristics_ch1: description_of_planned_arm: PBO FOR VELIPARIB 50 MG BID + PBO FOR CARBOPLATIN AUC 6 + PACLITAXEL 80 MG/M^2
characteristics_ch1.2: pretreatment_lymphnode_stage: N1-2 (biopsy positive)
extract_protocol_ch1: Pre-treatment biopsies were collected in RNAlater and total RNA was extracted.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Total RNA underwent whole transcriptome RNA sequencing (RNAseq) using RiboZero Gold rRNA depletion
extract_protocol_ch1.2: All samples were sequenced on an Illumina HiSeq 3000 with single-end 50bp reads
data_processing: Samples with >10 million unique reads were included for further analyses
data_processing.1: RNA-seq reads were aligned to the Ensembl release 76 top-level assembly with STAR version 2.0.4b.
data_processing.2: Gene counts were derived from the number of uniquely aligned unambiguous reads by Subread:featureCount version 1.4.5.
data_processing.3: Transcript counts were produced by Sailfish version 0.6.3.
data_processing.4: Sequencing performance was assessed for total number of aligned reads, total number of uniquely aligned reads, genes and transcripts detected, ribosomal fraction known junction saturation and read distribution over known gene models with RSeQC version 2.3.
data_processing.6: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: log2 normalized abundance data as a matrix table in a text file
contact_institute: Ohio State University Comprehensive Cancer Center
contact_address: Biomedical Research Tower, Room 512, 460 W. 12th Avenue
description_of_planned_arm:ch1: PBO FOR VELIPARIB 50 MG BID + PBO FOR CARBOPLATIN AUC 6 + PACLITAXEL 80 MG/M^2

characteristics_ch1: description_of_planned_arm: VELIPARIB 50 MG BID + CARBOPLATIN AUC 6 + PACLITAXEL 80 MG/M^2
characteristics_ch1.2: pretreatment_lymphnode_stage: N0 (clinically negative or biopsy negative)
extract_protocol_ch1: Pre-treatment biopsies were collected in RNAlater and total RNA was extracted.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Total RNA underwent whole transcriptome RNA sequencing (RNAseq) using RiboZero Gold rRNA depletion
extract_protocol_ch1.2: All samples were sequenced on an Illumina HiSeq 3000 with single-end 50bp reads
data_processing: Samples with >10 million unique reads were included for further analyses
data_processing.1: RNA-seq reads were aligned to the Ensembl release 76 top-level assembly with STAR version 2.0.4b.
data_processing.2: Gene counts were derived from the number of uniquely aligned unambiguous reads by Subread:featureCount version 1.4.5.
data_processing.3: Transcript counts were produced by Sailfish version 0.6.3.
data_processing.4: Sequencing performance was assessed for total number of aligned reads, total number of uniquely aligned reads, genes and transcripts detected, ribosomal fraction known junction saturation and read distribution over known gene models with RSeQC version 2.3.
data_processing.6: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: log2 normalized abundance data as a matrix table in a text file

characteristics_ch1.2: pretreatment_lymphnode_stage: N1-2 (biopsy positive)
extract_protocol_ch1: Pre-treatment biopsies were collected in RNAlater and total RNA was extracted.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Total RNA underwent whole transcriptome RNA sequencing (RNAseq) using RiboZero Gold rRNA depletion
extract_protocol_ch1.2: All samples were sequenced on an Illumina HiSeq 3000 with single-end 50bp reads
data_processing: Samples with >10 million unique reads were included for further analyses
data_processing.1: RNA-seq reads were aligned to the Ensembl release 76 top-level assembly with STAR version 2.0.4b.
data_processing.2: Gene counts were derived from the number of uniquely aligned unambiguous reads by Subread:featureCount version 1.4.5.
data_processing.3: Transcript counts were produced by Sailfish version 0.6.3.
data_processing.4: Sequencing performance was assessed for total number of aligned reads, total number of uniquely aligned reads, genes and transcripts detected, ribosomal fraction known junction saturation and read distribution over known gene models with RSeQC version 2.3.
data_processing.6: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: log2 normalized abundance data as a matrix table in a text file
contact_institute: Ohio State University Comprehensive Cancer Center
contact_address: Biomedical Research Tower, Room 512, 460 W. 12th Avenue
description_of_planned_arm:ch1: PBO FOR VELIPARIB 50 MG BID + CARBOPLATIN AUC 6 + PACLITAXEL 80 MG/M^2

title: 211009_RNAseq
characteristics_ch1: description_of_planned_arm: VELIPARIB 50 MG BID + CARBOPLATIN AUC 6 + PACLITAXEL 80 MG/M^2
characteristics_ch1.2: pretreatment_lymphnode_stage: N0 (clinically negative or biopsy negative)
extract_protocol_ch1: Pre-treatment biopsies were collected in RNAlater and total RNA was extracted.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Total RNA underwent whole transcriptome RNA sequencing (RNAseq) using RiboZero Gold rRNA depletion
extract_protocol_ch1.2: All samples were sequenced on an Illumina HiSeq 3000 with single-end 50bp reads
data_processing: Samples with >10 million unique reads were included for further analyses
data_processing.1: RNA-seq reads were aligned to the Ensembl release 76 top-level assembly with STAR version 2.0.4b.
data_processing.2: Gene counts were derived from the number of uniquely aligned unambiguous reads by Subread:featureCount version 1.4.5.
data_processing.3: Transcript counts were produced by Sailfish version 0.6.3.
data_processing.4: Sequencing performance was assessed for total number of aligned reads, total number of uniquely aligned reads, genes and transcripts detected, ribosomal fraction known junction saturation and read distribution over known gene models with RSeQC version 2.3.
data_processing.6: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: log2 normalized abundance data as a matrix table in a text file

characteristics_ch1.2: pretreatment_lymphnode_stage: N1-2 (biopsy positive)
extract_protocol_ch1: Pre-treatment biopsies were collected in RNAlater and total RNA was extracted.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Total RNA underwent whole transcriptome RNA sequencing (RNAseq) using RiboZero Gold rRNA depletion
extract_protocol_ch1.2: All samples were sequenced on an Illumina HiSeq 3000 with single-end 50bp reads
data_processing: Samples with >10 million unique reads were included for further analyses
data_processing.1: RNA-seq reads were aligned to the Ensembl release 76 top-level assembly with STAR version 2.0.4b.
data_processing.2: Gene counts were derived from the number of uniquely aligned unambiguous reads by Subread:featureCount version 1.4.5.
data_processing.3: Transcript counts were produced by Sailfish version 0.6.3.
data_processing.4: Sequencing performance was assessed for total number of aligned reads, total number of uniquely aligned reads, genes and transcripts detected, ribosomal fraction known junction saturation and read distribution over known gene models with RSeQC version 2.3.
data_processing.6: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: log2 normalized abundance data as a matrix table in a text file
contact_institute: Ohio State University Comprehensive Cancer Center
contact_address: Biomedical Research Tower, Room 512, 460 W. 12th Avenue
description_of_planned_arm:ch1: VELIPARIB 50 MG BID + CARBOPLATIN AUC 6 + PACLITAXEL 80 MG/M^2

extract_protocol_ch1: Pre-treatment biopsies were collected in RNAlater and total RNA was extracted.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Total RNA underwent whole transcriptome RNA sequencing (RNAseq) using RiboZero Gold rRNA depletion
extract_protocol_ch1.2: All samples were sequenced on an Illumina HiSeq 3000 with single-end 50bp reads
data_processing: Samples with >10 million unique reads were included for further analyses
data_processing.1: RNA-seq reads were aligned to the Ensembl release 76 top-level assembly with STAR version 2.0.4b.
data_processing.2: Gene counts were derived from the number of uniquely aligned unambiguous reads by Subread:featureCount version 1.4.5.
data_processing.3: Transcript counts were produced by Sailfish version 0.6.3.
data_processing.4: Sequencing performance was assessed for total number of aligned reads, total number of uniquely aligned reads, genes and transcripts detected, ribosomal fraction known junction saturation and read distribution over known gene models with RSeQC version 2.3.
data_processing.6: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: log2 normalized abundance data as a matrix table in a text file
contact_institute: Ohio State University Comprehensive Cancer Center
contact_address: Biomedical Research Tower, Room 512, 460 W. 12th Avenue

characteristics_ch1: description_of_planned_arm: VELIPARIB 50 MG BID + CARBOPLATIN AUC 6 + PACLITAXEL 80 MG/M^2
characteristics_ch1.2: pretreatment_lymphnode_stage: N0 (clinically negative or biopsy negative)
extract_protocol_ch1: Pre-treatment biopsies were collected in RNAlater and total RNA was extracted.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Total RNA underwent whole transcriptome RNA sequencing (RNAseq) using RiboZero Gold rRNA depletion
extract_protocol_ch1.2: All samples were sequenced on an Illumina HiSeq 3000 with single-end 50bp reads
data_processing: Samples with >10 million unique reads were included for further analyses
data_processing.1: RNA-seq reads were aligned to the Ensembl release 76 top-level assembly with STAR version 2.0.4b.
data_processing.2: Gene counts were derived from the number of uniquely aligned unambiguous reads by Subread:featureCount version 1.4.5.
data_processing.3: Transcript counts were produced by Sailfish version 0.6.3.
data_processing.4: Sequencing performance was assessed for total number of aligned reads, total number of uniquely aligned reads, genes and transcripts detected, ribosomal fraction known junction saturation and read distribution over known gene models with RSeQC version 2.3.
data_processing.6: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: log2 normalized abundance data as a matrix table in a text file
contact_institute: Ohio State University Comprehensive Cancer Center
